column5: With some steady minus temps in the forecast over the next week or so im getting super pumped to kick off my ice fishing season. Im hoping to be out on simcoe in two weeks. Do you guys think this is realistic? I certainly do. Can't wait for bacon wrapped perch.
The large part and K-bay will need a little longer IMO. The south end,well that's a different story!!!!.
ya im talking about cooks bay in particular. I figure the Whitie and Laker water will take a bit longer.
